  "key_invariants": [
    "Leaf package — no internal PCG imports allowed; reverse dependencies must not be introduced",
    "All metric names use pcg_dp_ prefix",
    "New metric dimension keys must be added to contract.go before use",
    "New span names must be added to contract.go before use",
    "Log keys are frozen in contract.go; reuse before adding",
    "High-cardinality values (file paths, fact IDs) belong in spans/logs, not metric labels",
    "Prometheus exporter is always active (regardless of OTLP configuration)",
    "OTEL_EXPORTER_OTLP_ENDPOINT controls whether OTLP gRPC exporters are created",
    "TraceHandler injects trace_id and span_id from active OTEL span context",
    "Observable gauges require RegisterObservableGauges to be called separately from NewInstruments"
  ]
}
